                <head>No. 579<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On June 17 riots and demonstrations broke out in the Soviet Sector of Berlin and
                    in East Germany. For documentation on these events, see <ref target="#d713"
                        >Documents 713</ref> ff.</p>
